title: Pre-season Patch 5.22 Jungle Garen New Meta???

embed.description: Decided to play some meta jungle Garen in the new pre-season patch 5.22. Actually, he works pretty good in the jungle now. Shithouse start though. You can also find on twitter @ https://twitter.com/shaunofdasheep And credit for the soundtrack goes to https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=yFUS_nTrXL8

body: Let's make him the new standard guys!!!  Garen needs our help!!!
